{"tid":1145021,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯是段譽 C朗是喬峰","createTime":"2019-05-08T12:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T14:49:06.000Z","uid":105472,"like":25,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6d78402229472735f446f481af5c8092c68c509b","tid":1145021,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"美斯一出世就在巴塞哩個皇宮 備受呵護<br />\n佩老沙維小白就恰如段譽嘅 北冥神功 六脈神劍 凌波微步<br />\n助佢天下無敵 但有睇過天龍八部都知<br />\n段譽雖然一生極其順利 但係臨陣對戰往往唔係如臂使指 得時威力無窮 唔得時候帶領巴塞比羅馬利記連追4球反cup<br />\n<br />\n相反 C朗就係喬峰 大戰時往往神勇百倍 帶領一堆嘍囉如丐幫幫眾時亦不落下風<br />\n隊友成日會轉 冇所謂嘅奇遇得到神功<br />\nC朗出道不久便死老豆 如喬峰嬰兒時期失去母親<br />\nC朗最似喬峰就係果種決心同領導才能<br />\n<br />\n註：段譽於天龍八部第十四回拜喬峰為契哥"},{"pid":"fd731e5fc7d359c64605eaa435d926d881075015","tid":1145021,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"9d573fc2946cc42baad3b18c4d5d494de352f11f","tid":1145021,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b2d7eb30b73519ebec6153ed158d956664e781e","tid":1145021,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"b2640f1c967bbe983a7b85044ba4776d70a99283","tid":1145021,"uid":33660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"好準"},{"pid":"7ecc4209297b8061331c103e924a121d0c187fdb","tid":1145021,"uid":105472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2640f1c967bbe983a7b85044ba4776d70a99283","tid":1145021,"uid":33660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"好準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"Thanks"},{"pid":"d5c72a4d4393873dea09f3aca1d4f9c7afa1b08f","tid":1145021,"uid":108618,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"唔好侮辱喬峰"},{"pid":"078783978ff29142e862a4b74f43638d457e4715","tid":1145021,"uid":45505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit